      "asbval:note": "Paper mentions CANOPUS as a complementary tool for compound-class annotation but does NOT describe parsing/validating CANOPUS web service results. The paper uses CANOPUS for compound class assignment (NPClassifier is mentioned for class assignment in Extended Data Fig. 10 context), but the specific task of parsing and validating CANOPUS web service JSON/tabular responses is not demonstrated or discussed in the paper. The card's research question describes a data-processing workflow that is not the focus of this paper.",
