    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/github-actions-workflow-execution/004",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "SIRIUS 4 was used to process LC\u2013MS/MS runs and MassIVE datasets provided in mzML or mzXML format.",
      "asbval:note": "SIRIUS is confirmed as a tool used in the paper for LC-MS/MS data analysis (passage 14). However, the claim about 'Build and Publish workflow' automating compilation and distribution is not mentioned in the paper. The paper uses SIRIUS as an analysis tool, not as a subject of GitHub Actions workflow testing. The card conflates SIRIUS (the scientific software) with a hypothetical CI/CD workflow for SIRIUS development, which is not discussed in this paper.",
