      "asbval:note": "Paper uses SIRIUS to process LC-MS/MS data, but does not describe REST API query payload construction or MSNovelist. SIRIUS is used for molecular formula determination and feature detection, not de-novo structure generation via REST API.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41587-021-01045-9",
