      "asbval:evidence_quote": "COSMIC complements compound class annotation tools such as CANOPUS45.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms CANOPUS exists and is used for compound-class annotation, but does NOT describe CANOPUS as a web service accepting fingerprint/spectrum queries or returning structured results to be validated. The paper does not detail CANOPUS's input/output interface or validation workflows. CANOPUS is mentioned only as a complementary tool, not as the subject of validation procedures.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41587-021-01045-9",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "partial",
